data.description:
Come see this Beautiful Log Home on 5 Acres. secluded wooded and quiet with an abundance of wildlife to view from your large front porch or back porch. 15 Minutes to downtown historical Washington, GA. 20 minutes to A. H. Stephens Georgia State Park Enjoy this homes large open floor plan where the kitchen, dining and great room  are all open to each other with a separate family. room. Home has master bedroom and bath. 2 more bedrooms Hall bath has tub/shower.
Included on property is an outbuilding/ shed, 2 stall horse barn with tack room, hay loft with water and electric. Partial pasture with plenty of acreage to expand.
